The expulsion allegedly urged by two Real Madrid players (Xabi Alonso and Sergio Ramos) in the match played on November 23 against Ajax in the Champions League has caused ink rivers to be written about whether such behavior is anti-sports or not and whether, eventually, both players were to be punished by UEFA.
